A [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]].

Ozcoin Pooled Mining Pty Ltd (ACN: 152509272) was founded June 9, 2011 (1.1).
This pool pays out using a proportional share reward system (your shares / total shares for the round) x (50BTC + transaction fees included in block)= % share of the rewards. 

##Reward distribution

* Proportional: 0% fee.
* Transaction fees included in blocks paid out to miners.
* Payout after 100 confirmations.
* Hourly payout automatic script (manual payout available for 2% fee)

##Extra Features

* Pin number required to change account settings 
* Getting Started page with lots of good info.
* Email on payout.
* Extensive stats.
* Friendly welcoming IRC chanel at irc.freenode.net #ozcoin or via the "WebChat" page on site.
* All found blocks listed with contributed shares and earnings.

